subject: RE: [EVP-ITC] Re: A few new ITC images
author: Frank Sumption
full_text:
That image on the group home page is an ITC type image, resulting from 
applying my random tuning technique to a TV set. The image has two features 
that that would indicate a paranormal source, one is the little "alien" on 
the guy's collar, and the second is an image of a wolf on the brim of his 
hat. Then there's also the shape of the face, longer than normal, in a 
typical MIB appearance.  I haven't done much work with the system yet.


Frank
